/*-----------------DOCUMENTATION-----------------------------------------------
Name: Dheeraj H K
Starting date: 02/11/2025
Ending date: 12/11/2025

Description:

This project is a Digital Image Steganography Tool written in C.
It allows the user to:

Encode (hide) a secret text file inside a BMP image

Decode (extract) the hidden text from the stego image

Validate file formats and handle errors

Preserve the original image quality

The program uses the Least Significant Bit (LSB) technique to hide data inside pixel bits.

Sample Input and Output:

Encoding

Input:

./a.out -e beautiful.bmp secret.txt stego.bmp


Output:

Encoding completed successfully.
Stego image saved as: stego.bmp


Decoding

Input:

./a.out -d stego.bmp output.txt


Output:

Decoding completed successfully.
Secret file extracted as: output.txt*/
